20 requiring Insurance Commissioner's approval of
mergers or acquisitions involving change in control
21 of a captive insurance company; requiring captive
insurance companies establish and maintain
22 administrative and accounting procedures; requiring
written approval for transfer of assets made with
23 respect to protected cell; requiring clear indication
in participant contact; requiring annual auditor
24 review; requiring contract identify protected cell;
