5 issuer.
6 For the purposes of this paragraph, "common ownership or
7 control" shall mean ownership of ten percent (10%) or more of the
8 voting securities or such other form of ownership or control as the
9 Insurance Commissioner may approve.
10 4. "Association" means a legal association of individuals,
11 corporations, partnerships, or associations that has been in
